# Projection-engine proof 3, restart half. Run against the profile created by
# proof3_recency.scn. The session restores the product-free Spiral score before
# the first frame, rebinds its opaque Mere source refs, and paints that score's
# positions through the ordinary canvas strategy buffer.
settle 40
key escape
assert nodes >= 14
assert visible
capture 01_score_restored

log projection proof 3 persisted score restored
